{"tid":2398712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美哈佛權威天文學家：外星文明2017年來過太陽系","createTime":"2021-02-07T13:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T14:26:55.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c11ee39d83b858b47c25664710b50d9a6a2cbf74","tid":2398712,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"發現地外智慧生命無疑會是人類歷史上最具顛覆性的事件，但若是科學界決定集體忽視恐<br />\n為地外文明已然造訪過的證據，又該如何？<br />\n <br />\n法新社報導，美國頂尖天文學家羅布（Avi Loeb）新書便提出上述假設。2017年一個不明<br />\n星際天體快速通過太陽系，羅布就主張，這個天體擁有高度不尋常的特徵，最簡單且最佳<br />\n的解釋，就是它屬於外星科技。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102070102.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202102070102.aspx&d=NdDBecmRZzhky7sLgKmJOS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=5ac20cf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202102070102.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"1e7a10a1ca2c1250370429220785f7fa40740d15","tid":2398712,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"咁又點 幾時核平支那豬"},{"pid":"c845bcd553928df105f428d339e7215462a12fdb","tid":2398712,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"問下nsa咪知囉"},{"pid":"7b96e92df1eda15198f374a49f1f37cbbf51ab73","tid":2398712,"uid":43204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"係喎之前侵又話解密既？"},{"pid":"d059fe21201c6053105facd07f4bc2e41fd849c9","tid":2398712,"uid":238475,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:26:55.000Z","msg":"五毛PR, 善用起底功能。"}]}